languages.text: Следующие несколько секунд пикт сервочерепа фиксирует только вспышки и грохот выстрелов. Когда звуки бойни стихают, уничтожены не только обезумевшие члены экипажа, но и часть священных когитаторов, окулусов и консолей мостика.

languages.text: The next few seconds of the servo-skull's pict contain nothing but flashes and gunshots. When the sounds of the massacre die down, the lunatics have been destroyed, as well as some of the sacred cogitators, oculi, and consoles on the bridge.

languages.text: En los siguientes segundos de la imagen del servocráneo solo hay destellos y disparos. Cuando los sonidos de la masacre callan por fin, los lunáticos han sido exterminados junto con algunos de los cogitadores, óculos y consolas sagrados del puente.

languages.text: 接下来的几秒钟内，伺服头骨的视讯画面中只剩下了闪光和枪声。当屠杀的声音终于平息时，疯子们已经一个都不剩了。舰桥上一部分神圣的沉思者、通讯装置与控制台也被摧毁了。
languages.original_text: The next few seconds of the servo-skull's pict contain nothing but flashes and gunshots. When the sounds of the massacre die down, the lunatics have been destroyed, as well as some of the sacred cogitators, oculi, and consoles on the bridge.

traits.locale_text: 接下来的几秒钟内，伺服头骨的视讯画面中只剩下了闪光和枪声。当屠杀的声音终于平息时，疯子们已经一个都不剩了。舰桥上一部分神圣的思考器、通讯装置与控制台也被摧毁了。

languages.text: 次の数秒のサーヴォスカルの映像では、フラッシュと銃声が確認できるのみだった。虐殺の音が静まると狂人達は始末され、ブリッジにある聖なる考算機も、オキュリも、コンソールも、すべてが一部破壊されていた。
languages.original_text: The next few seconds of the servo-skull's pict contain nothing but flashes and gunshots. When the sounds of the massacre die down, the lunatics have been destroyed, as well as some of the sacred cogitators, oculi, and consoles on the bridge.

traits.locale_text: 次の数秒のサーヴォスカルの映像では、フラッシュと銃声が確認できるのみだった。虐殺の音が静まると狂人達は始末され、ブリッジにある聖なる考算機も、オキュリも、コンソールも、すべてが一部破壊されていた。

languages.text: Die nächsten Sekunden des Bildes des Servoschädels bestehen nur aus Blitzen und Schüssen. Als die Geräusche des Massakers verstummen, sind die Verrückten zerstört, ebenso wie einige der heiligen Cogitatoren, Oculi und Konsolen auf der Brücke.
languages.original_text: The next few seconds of the servo-skull's pict contain nothing but flashes and gunshots. When the sounds of the massacre die down, the lunatics have been destroyed, as well as some of the sacred cogitators, oculi, and consoles on the bridge.

languages.text: Sur la pictocapture du servocrâne s'ensuivent quelques secondes remplies uniquement de l'éclat et du bruit des coups de feu. Quand le vacarme du massacre cesse, tous les fous ont succombé, de même que certains des cogitateurs sacrés, des oculi et des consoles sur le pont.
languages.original_text: The next few seconds of the servo-skull's pict contain nothing but flashes and gunshots. When the sounds of the massacre die down, the lunatics have been destroyed, as well as some of the sacred cogitators, oculi, and consoles on the bridge.

languages.text: Hizmelet fotosunun sonraki birkaç saniyesi, patlama ve silah seslerinden başka bir şey içermiyor. Katliam sesleri kesildiğinde, delilerin yanı sıra köprüdeki birkaç kutsal kavramsayar, oküler ve konsolun da yok olduğu görülüyor.
